.bloomberg.com/s/c/BkFHltnvECyjl2JtEmJY_Zmz6kfdnyNVhNeDrgp12zTKz0FS8fjyUA8Di0aZdvwa6x_UitTszBZ3d8KYd3qTFvhZP-9jYH72D7a9GisptLX-m6qAI1SPyxrfdRVm-RnzpBksufLTH0_tih2p_M5NhuQJC3wgJxSmqdQC4kY6VyuXARywdAZGJpGQ551hNSlOL0j-PrURDwP0uvRNYt6h_PFG7yhm_JChUt5A2pfPdml4JefU597-ohhSV3ZoRdrZCwBeby1aYhQutXz872_hpCpLYFQbd14PCKIFHtb19-kA7mTsTyCHhGf352F_RmkGaRPERtgvGt2B1ykdcu4qTNKMoLsQ6pcIgg/dqygWUO3ulxcv9ACy-fwHBGfoVmRScU-/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="意见 |特朗普正在抄袭中国。这是一个糟糕的主意。"&gt;在中国等地更为常见&lt;/a&gt;。在第二个任期内，特朗普表现出了极大的意愿，愿意在其政府认为对美国至关重要的私营企业中担任财务职务， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/R6duSB_UrT8QcWlwaqELnw889rAuC4L3O5oFhhkdNj4fuVFJ00i6R9PMMreBKrkhxxeg8aTlHfwBVzezOdqm9Zv90pgxtyF7Rzec7_QQGC4ra7K24d9FTXWYIUs8CM99noMZhd25uhwYEny_BkA4VOomURu1WGtu5vnr8owoJMrXbi5deWkPyBzpkIQdC0f-Tjn2neXKd4GQ0NvMkG_HVZgBIPbmFoYrtruXslTrUHhScnB9_aW5WXgmbX_BQPKrQNAj0bWrvRj0fRzHUX_VHLZoJcPFK0UqoG0JhaF1so-HMOnmtmMwfCVab_cY2vG24Gw3bQtD6EgQnArrCzbVI-Ia2XvAG_QwEeowED-wJ3dzVO83EGK0o0Y7tkGpVK1LFJiI17Cow_scCOrMYRfqeJAx-o3DfMNMx42Xpdj00MVnIybgFba5YlcmUPVYN96moFiZDtrq87SE8UMb84Ptvxp_qlH1THVftNODoeNwoAUGadnBrIPj273w22wIrXGblCI/HoX38mev8OHjBmm2Zcxnri1JlEKmf7qn/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="撇开政治不谈，英特尔欠我们关于其首席执行官的答案"&gt;例如芯片制造商英特尔&lt;/a&gt;。该策略引起了批评者的密切关注，他们质疑这种做法是否&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/I2IU2och0vuuu60QxLrCVdhbPLkihHHcI9WGTV0WJmiCFZgFRKj_YTEo8EJC6TUnz19YkXaYnMtGvCbSfWYloIU2oRo6lJJLcTK0JKwdfLPq0i8zSW4ygLWbdGd1k0OiTJGDljSv5busWjBquRSEW56bHGrvtVKBUt9bcfcEG54J-p6kbcJnvAHjhgtijlMl59bgdMG2Wyrluco16fp9-cO7By7nMLWkHq4yNNfnmQGW1Ip9yg05S3C00MZTU2PqnYo3MV_fkXkodBU0-0Ep82F2cf4kP-SGO-YE-3dW2vyK2pnuHfiUyO6Ab483mc-16ieztAzZ-I47BZQH_tIKXTRK-Qd8mgkyOo0BSKgvIiAymEd4XZoI6eJNC56HJaQB6TmrydXE9YEjNWqXOqUI8qqOcLk2cb4CAiGZkCWh1Z8qBg8nBefZ11LBlQf7Z1r47NpPCJtbhD__BxsX6ucCvcLpL4WQdltV3wcCX24E8fHlRO40y4G_MyMTFw/m8HF2B65XyAwG9k0lOw5TaL5pOK_3pNF/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style=